          "settings": {
            "title": "Quality Assurance &amp; Our Commitment to YOU",
            "use_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_y4eBkw": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At LaVivid Hair, <strong>quality</strong> is at the heart of everything we do.</p><p>Each piece is carefully inspected before it leaves our warehouse — from reviewing base materials and hair texture to confirming the exact color, length, density, and hairstyle.</p><p>If a quality concern ever arises, you can count on us to:</p><ul><li>Respond quickly and courteously.</li><li>Look into the matter with care and attention.</li><li>Work together with you to find the best solution — whether that means a replacement, adjustment, or refund.</li></ul><p>We stand behind our products and will always take responsibility for confirmed quality issues. Your trust means a great deal to us, and we are dedicated to ensuring you’re completely satisfied. If you have any questions or concerns, please <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>contact us </strong></span>anytime.<br/><br/></p>",
            "enlarge_text": true
          }
        }
      },
